div.div: Regression coefficients of the top models describing willow tit local recruitment in relation to caterpillar biomass.
div.p: The regression coefficients (Î²) and SE for models describing local recruitment of the willow tit derived from models F1, F2 and F3 in S12 Table. Coefficients are presented in the logit scale. Variables that had confidence intervals that do not include zero are in bold.
